"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"馬惜珍，又名馬奕盛，香港人，籍貫廣東潮陽和平鎮里美鄉，香港三合會福義興成員，與兄長馬惜如合創東方報業集團。1978年被控販毒，棄保潛逃至台灣，後一直被香港政府通緝。馬有三名兒子：馬澄坤、馬澄發、馬澄財，香港富豪馬廷強為其姪兒。 維基百科"},{"pid":"1333cd19cc94a8d01aeb24ba24765e92869f28b3","tid":1291441,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f86a4d93f3809a4825385fb9e68b3481b761c28","tid":1291441,"uid":33939,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKq0uX8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKq0uX8.jpg&h=051001de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇嘢好講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"冷笑左一下 好晞噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7ef44626cb3f97311a019f5e9271a69bc361b3","tid":1291441,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"東方呢篇野<br />\n引埋藍絲屌政府<br />\nwe connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb93d70a7e1decdbe2318d9e2cbe420f270f6b4","tid":1291441,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"身在漢營心在曹 都啱<br />\n一向認為劉備做嘅嘢好奸好狗 <br />\n曹軍先係正義一方"},{"pid":"3bc65e9ecd70d8bfce019d0f3f7524e1d34ddafe","tid":1291441,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:24:19.000Z","msg":"毒犯都唔應該有特赦"},{"pid":"0c3da168a58e9d01767e607b3b7d8c4029890b18","tid":1291441,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00e0703f45665ccfa62b4735803dc6c3d234179a","tid":1291441,"uid":165012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"東方你驚唔驚有班人擁有高學歷，隨時有機會入去你間野，「身在漢營心在曹」，潛伏搞破壞，重要關頭「亮劍」，殺個措手不及?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"之前好似有人講過，有義士入面做<br />\n想出啲正常非藍新聞，轉個頭就比人炒"},{"pid":"378de823a742b0fe52d3e7412e90a60a16f6c451","tid":1291441,"uid":39800,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黃毓民你條仆街肯離開東方未呀</strong></span></span>"}]}